[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16147] added 
``ShellWarning``
 (#16147)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16134] added interrupt check before each IR instruction (#16134)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16128] printed errors during stdlib testing (#16128)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16119] added 
``extern``
 for 
``nu``
 command (#16119)
@cptpiepmatz:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16161] fixed unwrapping 
``ShellErrorBridge``
 in 
``ByteStream::into_bytes``
 (#16161)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16160] made panic when converting other I/O errors to Nushell I/O errors (#16160)
@mgrachev:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16157] bumped 
``update-informer``
 to 
``v1.3.0``
 (#16157)
@fdncred:
